description:
DreamWorks All-Star Kart Racing Rally Pack is the ultimate kart racing experience for DreamWorks Animation fans young and young at heart with two new playable characters and exclusive content .  The DreamWorks All-Star Kart Racing Rally Pack includes:  

• Two exclusive playable characters: 
    o	Wolf from Puss in Boots: The Last Wish 
    o	Master Oogway from Kung Fu Panda

• Two exclusive character-inspired, playable karts chassis:
    o	1 for Wolf from Puss in Boots: The Last Wish 
    o	1 for Master Oogway from Kung Fu Panda

• Each exclusive kart chassis comes with 24 customization options:
    o	6 Kart designs options
    o	6 Engine options
    o	6 Wheel-style options
    o	6 Spoiler options
name: DreamWorks All-Star Kart Racing Rally Pack
